</pre></td><td class="rouge-code"><pre><span class="n">setTransformationMethod</span><span class="o">(</span><span class="nc">HideReturnsTransformationMethod</span><span class="o">.</span><span class="na">getInstance</span><span class="o">());</span>
</pre></td></tr></tbody></table></code></pre></div></div>

<p>显示<code class="highlighter-rouge">EditText</code>内容为密文:</p>

<div class="language-java highlighter-rouge"><div class="highlight"><pre class="highlight"><code><table class="rouge-table"><tbody><tr><td class="rouge-gutter gl"><pre class="lineno">1
</pre></td><td class="rouge-code"><pre><span class="n">setTransformationMethod</span><span class="o">(</span><span class="nc">PasswordTransformationMethod</span><span class="o">.</span><span class="na">getInstance</span><span class="o">());</span>
</pre></td></tr></tbody></table></code></pre></div></div>

